// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VillainOrRogue Text :
"P605329202" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>ATTENTION! SLAVES OF ARACHNOS! </color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>This loud phrase is broadcasted over...and over...and over again, almost forcing your attention. You go to a place where you can clearly hear the broadcast. The man broadcasting the message finally gets underway...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>This is Marshal Blitz, leader of the Rogue Arachnos in Warburg. For far too long we have not been taken seriously by Arachnos - today, however, that will all change! My soldiers have taken an Arachnos base and everyone in it hostage - its scientists, soldiers, and Longbow prisoners. <br><br> We have a list of demands that, if they are not met, will result in the destruction of this base! Any Arachnos operative listening had best take this seriously, for this is the dawning of a new age in Arachnos!  </scale></font></color><br> <br>It looks like the Rogue Arachnos have finally made their move. If there are Longbow prisoners in that base, you can bet that some heroes will be showing up to save them. <br> <br> You could always find out the location of the base, break into it, save everyone in there, then make off with the information in the base as well - Arachnos won't know that it was your doing anyway. <br><br> Of course, if heroes are looking for the base, you could go to another area of St. Martial, plant a fake recorder to make them think that is the location of the base, then wipe out any heroes who fall for the trap. "
// Answer Text :
"P2402448443" "VILLAIN: Trap Longbow and defeat any heroes who fall for it!"
// Answer Text :
"P4210119667" "ROGUE: Stop the Rogue Arachnos and steal any information."
// Page Vigilante Text :
"P2063606614" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>ATTENTION! SLAVES OF ARACHNOS! </color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>This loud phrase is broadcasted over...and over...and over again, almost forcing your attention. You go to a place where you can clearly hear the broadcast. The man broadcasting the message finally gets underway...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>This is Marshal Blitz, leader of the Rogue Arachnos in Warburg. For far too long we have not been taken seriously by Arachnos - today, however, that will all change! My soldiers have taken an Arachnos base and everyone in it hostage - its scientists, soldiers, and Longbow prisoners. <br><br> We have a list of demands that, if they are not met, will result in the destruction of this base! Any Arachnos operative listening had best take this seriously, for this is the dawning of a new age in Arachnos!  </scale></font></color><br> <br>The Rogue Arachnos have made their move - it's about time. How long have they held an entire island to themselves without doing anything? Maybe once Marshal Blitz is in power, things would change for the Rogue Isles. <br><br>  But you don't care about change in this land of scum - you care about results. <br><br> If Blitz and his men are stopped, then nothing will result from all of this aside from his men being pushed back into Warburg. <br><br> If they blow up that base, then it means more...interesting things will come about. Arachnos will suffer, Longbow will suffer, and those are the two groups that need to be shown suffering the most. <br><br> You'll just need to make sure that Longbow doesn't stop this...valuable lesson from happening."
// Answer Text :
"P3107976562" "VILLAIN: Stop the Longbow rescue squad."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
"P4254791821" "Now is not a good time to investigate this tip.  Wait until you are within the streets of the Rogue Isles before you attempt any investigation."
// Answer Text :
"P385518726" "Investigate this tip later"
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


