// Page VillainOrRogue Text :
"P2859301267" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Mask Covered in Saliva</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You found a Carnival of Shadows mask covered in saliva - the monstrous kind. You notice bite marks as well as holes made by a corrosive substance - Arachnoid acid. Investigating further, you find out the following...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Earlier today, the Carnival of Shadows were throwing one of their 'parties' in the main street of St. Martial. They were causing their usual chaos and destruction, until one of the Seneschals made the mistake of putting her torch too close to the wrong truck. The vehicle exploded, creating a large crater, which exposed a hidden Arachnoid cave underground! <br><br> Many of the Carnival fell in to the lair before it was sealed up by Arachnos. Now the Arachnoids are rampaging in one of the casinos, while the other Carnies are trapped in that cavern.  </scale></font></color><br> <br> The Carnival of Shadows always seem to take their parties too far. Arachnos is too busy trying to contain the Arachnoid threat in the streets of St. Martial, meaning that casino is still crawling with Arachnoids. <br><br> Going in there and saving the patrons and manager of the casino would earn you their gratitude - but more so, you would have free reign over taking the money from the casino for yourself. <br><br> Then again...those Carnies are still probably fighting the Arachnoids in that lair. But if someone were to go in there and finish them off...well, that would be less Carnies around to keep their leader, Vanessa DeVore, powered. "
// Answer Text :
"P3048754686" "VILLAIN: Finish off the Carnies in the Arachnoid cave!"
// Answer Text :
"P966078867" "ROGUE: Save and rob the Casino!"
// Page Vigilante Text :
"P802493482" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Mask Covered in Saliva</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You found a Carnival of Shadows mask covered in saliva - the monstrous kind. You notice bite marks as well as holes made by a corrosive substance - Arachnoid acid. Investigating further, you find out the following...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Earlier today, the Carnival of Shadows were throwing one of their 'parties' in the main street of St. Martial. They were causing their usual chaos and destruction, until one of the Seneschals made the mistake of putting her torch too close to the wrong truck. The vehicle exploded, creating a large crater, which exposed a hidden Arachnoid cave underground! <br><br> Many of the Carnival fell in to the lair before it was sealed up by Arachnos. Now the Arachnoids are rampaging in one of the casinos, while the other Carnies are trapped in that cavern.  </scale></font></color><br> <br> The Carnival of Shadows...a group of clowns that don't deserve a second glance, let alone any mercy. They're stuck in that cavern full of Arachnoids now, scared and waiting for their 'mistress' to come save them. <br><br> Knowing the Carnival, that will happen...eventually. Vanessa DeVore won't let one of her precious souls be lost to the beasts. <br><br> Someone needs to make sure that the Carnies in that cave aren't saved. They must be made to <color>suffer</color> for everything they've done...they must be an example to anyone out there. <br><br> An example of what YOU will do to those who don't do right by you."
// Answer Text :
"P2801508088" "VILLAIN: Take down the Carnies in the Arachnoid cave!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


