// Page VillainOrRogue Text :
"P3170876855" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Darrin Wade's Wish List</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a list of artifacts that are wanted by Darrin Wade, along with some notes made on it...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Hardcase - <br><br> It's interesting, the artifacts that Wade wants. He's definitely up to something, that's for sure, given how much he's willing to pay for them. When I did some research, I found out that there are two identical sets of these artifacts. The true set is being held by the Circle of Thorns - the other is in the possession of the Carnival of Shadows. <br><br> The thing is, the Carnies have the fake set - I don't know <i>why</i> they do, but they do. But you wouldn't know they're fake until you try to use them - at which point they would blow up in your face. </scale></font></color><br> <br> Darrin Wade, a newcomer to the Isles, is definitely someone who has layers upon layers of plans up his sleeve. These artifacts would probably further them. It's safe to assume all of these plans will lead to him obtaining some sort of immense power, given what you've heard from him. <br><br> If the artifacts that the Carnies have <i>really</i> aren't genuine, you could try to steal those and sell it to Darrin Wade - he'll never know that they're fake until they explode, and even then, you can cover it up so that no one knows that the true artifacts didn't just...explode upon use. <br><br> Or...you can beat Wade to the punch and raid the Circle's lair to take the artifacts for yourself. What is he going to do about it? Send an ex-Midnighter after you?"
// Answer Text :
"P3356402634" "VILLAIN: Steal Darrin Wade's artifacts for yourself"
// Answer Text :
"P338338066" "ROGUE: Steal then sell the fake artifacts to Wade."
// Page Vigilante Text :
"P3281035594" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Darrin Wade's Wish List</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a list of artifacts that are wanted by Darrin Wade, along with some notes made on it...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Hardcase - <br><br> It's interesting, the artifacts that Wade wants. He's definitely up to something, that's for sure, given how much he's willing to pay for them. When I did some research, I found out that there are two identical sets of these artifacts. The true set is being held by the Circle of Thorns - the other is in the possession of the Carnival of Shadows. <br><br> The thing is, the Carnies have the fake set - I don't know <i>why</i> they do, but they do. But you wouldn't know they're fake until you try to use them - at which point they would blow up in your face. </scale></font></color><br> <br> Darrin Wade, an ex-Midnighter. You can't help but wonder why he was shunned by their organization. You almost feel a certain...kinship to him, really, knowing a thing or two about organizations not understanding certain...measures that must be taken. <br><br> These artifacts he has listed here seem like they'd be very powerful in the right hands. <br><br> It's just too bad for him those aren't...his hands. Imagine what you could do with these artifacts. The power you could wield, the fear you could strike into your enemies, into anyone who would dare stand in your way! <br><br> This is too good of an opportunity to just pass up for some ex-Midnighter to take advantage of."
// Answer Text :
"P2690017876" "VILLAIN: Take Darrin Wade's artifacts for yourself!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


